                  </persName>
            . I am an headborough of St. Luke's. On Wednesday last I apprehended her; I searched her, and found the purse upon her.</p>
               <p>The property produced and identified.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. When I came out of the White Horse I kicked the purse before me, but there was nothing in it.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18090412-70-verdict431" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090412-70-verdict431" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
